    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence and high decision consequence. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device within the defined COU.",
